“If you want a Bentley Bacalar, you’re too late.

Each of the 12 individuals worldwide who purchased the $2 million open-top two-seater has already spent many months developing personalized exterior paint schemes, unique tones for the Beluga leather seats, and detailed stitching patterns.”

Hannah Elliot highlights just a few of the reasons why the #Bentley #Bacalar was so in demand for @bloombergbusiness 
___

This model is in a pre-production state.
